name: CarryOnGuide
0:
”Alexa, open carry on guide”
”Alexa, ask carry on guide to lookup American Airlines carry on policy”
”Alexa, open carry on guide and find out what carry on I bring onto JetBlue”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: carry on guide
des:
When traveling why add stress. Ask Alexa to find the carry on policies of your airline while packing. Don't get stuck with paying unnecessary baggage fees at the airport.

Sizes and weights are all taken directly from the airline's website as of September 2018.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
